address.streetAddress: The Sandstone Plan, Weser Creek at Heybourne Meadows

location.fullValue: The Sandstone Plan, Weser Creek at Heybourne Meadows

data.description: Great opportunity to own one of the original model homes in Winhaven.  Original Owners.  Located next to the open space, ponds, and grass, the homes backyard is nicely landscaped.  This 4 bedroom(which has the den option off of living room) 2 bath home is very spacious with a large kitchen and tons of counter space.  Wood flooring in the entry/hall/dining/family room areas.  Large attic space for storage.  Ideally located close to shopping, restaurants, and medical. Home has original shake roof, which looks to be in decent shape with no leaking.  Based on the age, not sure if this will go FHA/VA and Seller will not replace the roof.  Home is in good shape, but will be sold in As Is condition.  Easy to show, call to let me know who and when will be showing.  Lockbox on front door.
